# knowledge.md

Global personal knowledge base. Auto-loaded at the start of every OpenCode session.
Apply these preferences in all projects without being asked.

**Setup:** Add this file path to `opencode.jsonc` instructions field:

```jsonc
{
  "instructions": [
    "~/.agents/knowledge.md"
  ]
}
```

